title: Discografia Chiara Civello
description:
Fantastic Italian Jazz - Pop singer, sings in English, Italian, and Portuguese, a lot of Brazilian Influence. According to Tony Bennett, the best Jazz singer of her generation.
Torrent includes her two albums, Last Quarter Moon (2005) and The Space Between (2007) - only released in Italy -, plus some extra songs she recorded as a guest for Nicola Conte and Juan Luis Guerra. Enjoy!
